OL,5, A man has been arrested on live TV in  
OL,6, the US state of Indiana after his      
OL,7, four-year-old son, appearing to wear a 
OL,8, nappy, was seen waving a gun.          
OL,10,FShane Osborne, 45, was charged with    
OL,11,Fneglect after neighbours reported a    
OL,12,Fchild in a hallway carrying what they  
OL,13,Fbelieved to be a handgun, police said. 
OL,15,FThe arrest was filmed on the TV show On
OL,16,FPatrol: Live.                          
OL,18,FThe show aired surveillance video      
OL,19,Fallegedly showing the boy playing with 
OL,20,Fa weapon and even pulling the trigger. 
